			<div class="plane2 plane2_download">
            	<p>赶快加入我们吧：<a href="https://www.dface.cn/a?v=130">Android版</a><a href="https://www.dface.cn/a?v=130">App Store</a></p>
			</div>
		</div>
		<div class="mainright">
			<a href="http://www.dface.cn" target="_blank"><img src="/admin/image/share_weibo/logo.png" class="logo" alt=""/></a>
			<div class="plane3">
				<div class="wordstyle mb10 bold">此时此刻，我们在这里</div>
				脸脸--基于现场的移动社交
			</div>
			<div class="plane4">
				<a href="http://www.dface.cn/a?v=130" alt="iPhone版" class="btn1"></a>
				<a href="http://www.dface.cn/a?v=130" alt="android版" class="btn2"></a>
				<img src="/admin/image/share_weibo/qrcode.png" alt="" height="128" class="dow_2code"/>
			</div>
		</div>
		<div class="clear1"></div>
		<div class="footer2"><a href="http://www.dface.cn">脸脸©2014</a></div>
	</div>
